{"tid":513930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"冷卻左嘅心，可唔可以重新燃燒","createTime":"2017-12-30T05:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T09:43:36.000Z","uid":23170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e75d403106785dd1a16dd186085fe1d047378e06","tid":513930,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"雖然過去經常都仲會諗起，但係當改變左，都無辦法返返去以前。我成日喺到諗，我同佢都已經變左做第二個人，再遇上，大家都只不過係認識對方名字嘅陌生人。再遇上，真係會重燃到昔日嗰份愛火？記掛，都係當初嘅嗰個人，再遇上，真係仲會見到佢嘅影子？睇清左，先明白，當初有幾傻。無一個人係因為我而生存，真實世界唔同故事，無一個人嘅性格係完美地配合卻又永恆不變，就算曾經相襯，當時光逝去，一齊都可以改變。記住過去嘅你，但唔好再諗住依家嘅你會仲一樣。人，去到最後，都只係會不斷改變。"},{"pid":"b6859baba53dd8574602e2b36dab1650cfe915c7","tid":513930,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76a5c0e0848804c2a2b59d327f0d2faa087780ad","tid":513930,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b6859baba53dd8574602e2b36dab1650cfe915c7","tid":513930,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"wahahahahahahahahahahahaha, 屌，肥絲你點可以咁搞笑㗎，笑到我肚都痛呀，hahahajajajajajajahahahahahahahahahahaha<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/001/251/868/351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Foriginal%2F001%2F251%2F868%2F351.jpg&h=c41f407b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTSQj4P1W4dz1sA6oAGKxNQ3BcyFbZB_seC4BIAiA5nxzDcIK3lLA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcTSQj4P1W4dz1sA6oAGKxNQ3BcyFbZB_seC4BIAiA5nxzDcIK3lLA&h=0b5e88db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ae2c9de51e8c2699ac05463fd14f157a5a866d5","tid":513930,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:05:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"5d0687d8763184dba845d3b3b98abe7560